# Never commit local secrets (smoke-test credentials, scratch notes with tokens, etc.)
*.local
*.local.md
smoke-test-credentials.local.md
# The shared scheme's Test action carries smoke-test credentials as environment
# variables. If the current blanket `Planner.xcodeproj` ignore is ever narrowed,
# this explicit rule keeps scheme files (and therefore those secrets) out of git.
Planner.xcodeproj/xcshareddata/xcschemes/*.xcscheme
*.xcscheme
